    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your weapons rend through flesh, sinew, and bone alike. The creature damaged by your brutal strike has their damage reduction reduced by an amount equal to 1/2 your base attack bonus (minimum 1). This reduction lasts for as long as the target has the battered condition. This reduction does not stack with itself.</p>\n<p>The benefits of this talent are halved (minimum 1) when applied to damage reduction that cannot be overcome or is overcome only by epic weapons (such as DR 3/&#8211; or DR 20/epic).</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> If you possess mythic ranks, the benefits of this talent are no longer halved against DR/epic.</p>\n",
